Description:
In front of a big heron’s head sculpture, you find a feline merchant boasting about the sacred Basthet’s relics he is selling, blessed by the goddess herself. From her sacred paws to your hands!

He says that you look like fine connoisseurs of relics and ancient artifacts and that you should take a look to his wares.

There are some items that catch your eye.
DescriptionAction: Will you risk to be tempted by the merchant?
